20 21 22 23 24 25
The purpose of today's meeting in Austin is to give interested persons an opportunity to present their views or questions on the three options APHIS has presented for comment, as well as to present other possible options for administering the imported fire ant program, in light of reduced funding.
3 1 2 3 4 5 6 Notice of today's meeting was published in the Federal Register on March 2, on pages 11,281 through 11,283, and extra copies of the notice are available at the registration table.
