46 1 2 3 4 5 6 This gives us a big problem during droughty years that we've experienced here in the last three years, the last three summers, where we have a major need to save cattle in West Texas and other western states, where we don't have hay to ship them because we can't assure that we can treat it and make those hay bales ant free.
