7 8 9 10 11 12 13
exact every persuasion that you possibly can to see that funding can be restored to the federal government's portion of this fire ant quarantine program.
And with my compliments, I wish you luck, and I hope that you can bring back an effective funding that might even grow over subsequent years.
This is a very effective effort, one that's extremely unique in the cooperation that
14 15 16 17 18 19
you have with other states.
And we appreciate you and all that you're doing.
